                    "effect": "The stone\u2019s light begins to pulse. You can choose the rate of the pulse between slow, moderate, and fast. If the linked stone is within 15 miles, its center begins to glow in the same color and pulse at the same rate. You can use this activation to end the pulsing caused by a linked stone.",
